Package se.kvirkel.tankwars.game

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    TWBullet
    Bullet class with bullet specific information
    TWGame
    main class of TankWars game; contains each gamestate and some static variables and methods
    TWGameClient
    GameClient class; handles all the local calculations on the playing client also forwards information to the connected NetworkClient
    TWGameEntity
    the abstract shell for every entity in the game.
    TWGameRenderer
    Client painter, draws everything on the client window
    TWGameServer
    Game server class.
    TWMapMenuState
    the state where you choose the desired map
    TWMenuState
    Menu state GameState; the main menu containing a gamelog and the main menu options
    TWPlayer
    Playerclass, contains useful information about every player
    TWServerUpdater
    A simple runnable class updating the server
